sources.title: Stand By Me Doraemon 1-2 (English Dubs)
sources.description: I found these dubs of those movies from the Complete English Dub collection of Doraemon (that features the Watch Disney XD rips of the series) This dub was made by Bang Zoom! Studios (aka Bang Zoom! Entertainment) after 6 years of production of the Doraemon dub on Disney XD, this was also commissioned to Netflix too. Encoded using HandBrake February 11, 2025 EDIT: Added the first Stand by Me Doraemon movie.
